        {
            "id": 5980466,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉台積電暌違2個月的千元價重現 但沒站穩 拖累指數震盪翻小黑",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國川普政府對中國關稅政策逐漸趨緩和且明朗，激勵美股今晨收高，同時，川普訪中東又帶來對波音及 AI 晶片銷售的佳音，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 今 (15) 日早盤重新站上暌違 2 個月的 1000 元大關 ，推升電子股早盤上揚並占成交比重達 68.18%，指數以 21776.65 點開出後走高，大盤電子及金融股都呈現上漲態勢。預估全場成交值 4076 億元。不過，台積電千元關未站穩，早盤指數一度落在平盤下。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>資深證券分析師簡伯儀指出，近期台股指數創下 17306.97 低點後跌深反彈，目前面臨半年線及年線壓力區，雖然市場觀望氣氛稍減，但短線解套壓力將造成 大盤的壓力。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>資深證券分析師黃漢成指出，近日市場各企業發布的首季財報及 4 月營收，股價也在反映業績表現強勁個股如聯策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6658:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6658\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6658-TW</a>)、台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>) 等，但大盤短線上檔壓力仍大。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台北股市大盤今早盤開在 21776.65 點，最高 21821.01 點，最低 21771.36 點，預估全場成交值超過 4000 億元，市場專家認為台股今天將呈現高檔震盪格局。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股早盤台積電一度站上 1000 元走強、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 走勢偏弱、廣達 (2382-TW ) 今年資本支出將達 200 億元走高。蘋果概念股大立光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>) 、玉晶光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3406:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3406\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3406-TW</a>) 股價在平盤上下震盪、亞光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3019:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3019\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3019-TW</a>) 早盤獲資金強勢拉抬小漲。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同時，在在航太零組件個股晟田 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4541:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4541\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4541-TW</a>)、駐龍 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4572:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4572\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4572-TW</a>) 及寶一 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8222:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8222\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8222-TW</a>) 早盤開高，但市場賣壓不斷湧出壓抑股價。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IC 載板類股走勢上，欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)、南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>) 下跌，但景碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>) 小漲，表現相對強勢；但開高遇賣盤進行調節，而貨櫃航運長榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2603-TW</a>) 上漲 ，萬海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2615:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2615\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2615-TW</a>) 及陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>) 早盤同步走高，但市場賣壓也不斷壓抑股價表現。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今晨美股收盤主要指數表現上，美股<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>下跌 89.37 點，或 0.21%，收 42,051.06 點。 <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>指數上漲 136.72 點，或 0.72%，收 19,146.81 點。<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a> 指數上漲 6.03 點，或 0.1%，收 5,892.58 點。<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數上漲 29.38 點，或 0.60%，收 4,960.74 點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>成分股方面，輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 勁揚 4.16% ；應用材料 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>) 漲 0.64%；博通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>) 跌 0.13%；高通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>) 上漲 1.08% ；AMD (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>) 強漲 4.68%；美光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>) 下跌 1.66%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而台積電 ADR (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 收盤上 漲 0.40%</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
